季，阿奎莱拉和格林再次回归，与列维和谢尔顿二人共同参与节目。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1707280/voice-christina-aguilera-cee-lo-green-deals.jhtml | title=Christina Aguilera Returning To 'The Voice,' Cee Lo Green Near Deal | publisher=''[[Viacom|Viacom]]'' | work=[[MTV_News|MTV News]] | date=May 14, 2013 | accessdate=May 15, 2013 | author=Gil Kaufmann | archive-date=2013-10-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131024090224/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1707280/voice-christina-aguilera-cee-lo-green-deals.jhtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>而第六季则仍由夏奇拉和亚瑟小子二人与列维和谢尔顿共同担任导师。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/05/16/the-voice-judges-shakira/ | title='The Voice': Shakira, Usher, Cee Lo ALL coming back | publisher=''[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]]'' | work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date=May 16, 2013 | accessdate=May 18, 2013 | author=James Hibberd | archive-date=2014-02-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140216201416/http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/05/16/the-voice-judges-shakira/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年2月，希洛·格林在接受[[艾倫·狄珍妮|艾倫·狄珍妮]]采访时表示，他将不会回归节目的第七季。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/cee-lo-green-im-not-681487 |title=Cee Lo Green: I'm Not Returning to 'The Voice' (Video) |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archive-date=2014-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318063534/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/cee-lo-green-im-not-681487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年3月31日，节目组宣布[[法瑞尔·威廉姆斯|法瑞尔·威廉姆斯]]将从第七季起加盟节目，填补格林离开后留下的空缺，<ref name="pharrell season 7">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2014/03/31/pharrell-williams-named-coach-for-season-7-of-the-voice/249537/|title=Pharrell Williams Named Coach for Season 7 of 'The Voice'|last=Bibel|first=Sara|accessdate=March 31, 2014|publisher=Zap2it|archive-date=2014-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403053039/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2014/03/31/pharrell-williams-named-coach-for-season-7-of-the-voice/249537/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同时[[關·史蒂芬妮|關·史蒂芬妮]]也在第七季中代替怀孕在身的阿奎莱拉担任导师一职，<ref name="gwen season 7">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2608219/Gwen-Stefani-join-The-Voice-judge-pregnant-Christina-Aguilera-sits-season.html|title=Gwen Stefani to join The Voice as a judge while a pregnant Christina Aguilera sits out the next season|work=Daily Mail|date=2014-04-19|accessdate=2014-04-19|archive-date=2014-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420040527/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2608219/Gwen-Stefani-join-The-Voice-judge-pregnant-Christina-Aguilera-sits-season.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>阿奎莱拉则于第八季回归节目。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/588215/the-voice-bringing-back-christina-aguilera-for-season-8|title=The Voice Bringing Back Christina Aguilera for Season 8|work=E!Online|date=2014-10-14|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015024910/http://www.eonline.com/news/588215/the-voice-bringing-back-christina-aguilera-for-season-8|dead-url=no}}</ref>
[[File:Carson_Daly.jpg|thumb]]
节目自开播起便由[[卡森·达利|卡森·达利]]主持。<ref name="carson">{{cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/carson-daly-host-nbcs-voice-95200 | title=Carson Daly to Host NBC's 'The Voice' | publisher=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' | date=February 1, 2011 | accessdate=April 2, 2011 | archive-date=2014-01-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101215752/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/carson-daly-host-nbcs-voice-95200 | dead-url=no }}</ref>第一季中，{{link-en|艾莉森·海斯利普|Alison Haislip}}担任了“后台、在线及[[社交媒体|社交媒体]]联络员”，负责在后台采访选手和导师，并追踪选手的社交网络信息。<ref name="haislip">{{cite web | url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2011/03/28/nbc-names-alison-haislip-g4s-attack-of-the-show-as-backstage-online-and-social-media-correspondent-for-new-musical-competition-series-the-voice-111310/20110328nbc03/ | title=NBC Names Alison Haislip, G4's "Attack of the Show!", As Backstage Online and Social Media Correspondent for New Musical Competition Series "The Voice" | publisher=''The Futon Critic'' | date=March 28, 2011 | accessdate=April 2, 2011}}</ref>第二季中则由[[克里斯蒂娜·米莲|克里斯蒂娜·米莲]]接替此职。连续主持三季后，米莲因参加《[[与星共舞_(美国真人秀)|与星共舞]]》而退出节目第五季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/s148/the-voice/news/a509858/christina-milian-not-returning-to-the-voice.html|title=Christina Milian not returning to 'The Voice'|work=Digital Spy|date=2013-08-26|accessdate=2014-03-24|archive-date=2014-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324075511/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/s148/the-voice/news/a509858/christina-milian-not-returning-to-the-voice.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后的节目便由卡森·达利一人主持。

